<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>﴿فِجَاجًا﴾ <span class="c4">[نوح: ٢٠]</span>: الطُّرُقُ الواسِعَةُ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
